    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three people and a dog are waiting for the bus made of light. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Their wish to turn their lives around attracts a myriad of fireflies... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this short hidden object game, you experience the story of 3 people and a dog. Why are they waiting for the bus made of light? What do they wish for? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decipher their stories and find the matching firefly from various glowing fireflies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247490/extras/ee2edf921c1ed91f5ce491ad77c28da3.poster.avif?t=1734018921\" width=620 height=378 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247490/extras/ee2edf921c1ed91f5ce491ad77c28da3.webm?t=1734018921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247490/extras/ee2edf921c1ed91f5ce491ad77c28da3.mp4?t=1734018921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featurelist of the Demo: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 1 character fully playable</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- unique fireflies each level </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- relatable story</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy!</p>",
